He turnedthere was no one whom he could suspect,
except the clergyman, and the old man. He went
forthwith
to Oscar, and told him what he had heard.
Oscar pressed his hand. The warning
was
friendly;
regard it, Harold. Beware of me. I say the same.
Indeed
,
