.
`Young man,' said she, `my masterSalisbury
CumberlandHarold, or whatever may be thy name,
God is good
. Remember him. Mayest thou have all
the virtues of thy bloodnone of its follies!'
`Follies, dame,' said Mr. Hammond, `speak plainly
to the young man. This is no time for mincing
